[G7]I saw a teardrop on a [C]rose
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[G7]A sobbing tear that follows parting
[C]Holds all the pain that [G7]sorrow knows
[C]A trusting heart had just [C7]been [F]shattered
